{"tid":2261383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建制操控 地址屬秘書公司","createTime":"2020-10-28T09:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T11:12:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb17378b2eb7e1d1b382dbde182a6cbe3116a4d","tid":2261383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/6RZG2IYR3NHZFLEET7EHPWKZD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2F6RZG2IYR3NHZFLEET7EHPWKZD4%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7BPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=9a6f79ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2F6RZG2IYR3NHZFLEET7EHPWKZD4%2F&h=04573a9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/6RZG2IYR3NHZFLEET7EHPWKZD4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n建制操控 地址屬秘書公司<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6JWImu_k4a4dqzkVmczA8Hd0kYY=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6Z25GUKQKJH43APGGRISGNCXQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6JWImu_k4a4dqzkVmczA8Hd0kYY%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6Z25GUKQKJH43APGGRISGNCXQM.jpg&h=2caff889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■卓思工作室的登記地址原為一間秘書公司。<br />\n<br />\n雖然黃建新聲稱公民社會研究所與政黨並無關係，但記者調查發現，研究所背後的公司董事亦有深厚建制背景，過去亦活躍於從事票站調查。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鍾劍華：難反映真正意見<br />\n<br />\n翻查公司註冊處資料，持有公民社會研究所公眾號的公司「卓思工作室有限公司」，其董事和股東是港人譚邃長，他是建制組織「香港青年協進會」的副主席，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電話無人接聽<br />\n<br />\n記者到訪卓思工作室位於旺角的註冊地址，發現原來是一會計師樓兼秘書公司，職員聲稱卓思只是其客戶。卓思收到秘書公司轉交的查詢後以電郵表示，自己並非「公民社會研究所」的負責機構，只提供微信公眾號申請服務，着記者致電研究所查詢。但卓思提供的電話號碼一直無人接聽。<br />\n<br />\n譚邃長過去曾協助過建制派做意見調查。2008年，本報曾揭露多個建制背景的調。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"9c9eab2344401f7aa3525f33d8e78378ec5b044f","tid":2261383,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:05:04.000Z","msg":"近排真係精彩，越爆越多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadb301a5c16cc6779bdbf5b404c33967dbfb715","tid":2261383,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}